<H3> <TI>   Hydrogeological Effects of Underground Nuclear Explosions </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  947N0008A Moscow DOKLADY AKADEMII NAUK in Russian Vol 332 No 
3, Sep 93 pp 372-374 </F>

<F P=103> 947N0008A </F>
